the new high lander will be unveiled at the north american international auto show in the next few days .
today &apos;s exhibition is for the media only .
Ford 's redesigned f - 150 pickup won the title of " wind and clouds truck of the year . "
according to lee Anse , president of a Ford sales department , Ford 's f - 150 is the best - selling car in the world . the 2004 f - 150 model was redesigned . it reached an all - time high in december last year , selling a total of 84,600 cars .
