the free trade zone of the americas stretches from Alaska in the north to argentina in the south . it is claimed to be the largest free trade zone in the world , with a total market population of about 800 million and a total production volume of as high as $ 13 trillion .
however , at the end of the two - day summit , Argentine president Kissina issued a statement criticizing the us plan , saying that the problems in the americas could not be solved by establishing a free trade zone alone .
