over the past several hundred years since the birth of the intellectual property system , especially since the industrial revolution , one major invention after another of epoch - making significance has been spawned .
in the past two decades , the intellectual property system has become a basic legal system and an important policy means for various countries to promote technological innovation , and has played an important role in invigorating the economy and enhancing international competitiveness .
at present , with the rapid development of science and technology and economic globalization , the creation , possession , and use of knowledge and intellectual resources , as well as the quantity and quality of intellectual property rights , have become an important foundation for all countries to participate in international competition .
therefore , strengthening international exchanges and cooperation in ipr protection is of great significance to the establishment of a just and rational new international economic order and the promotion of world economic prosperity and development .
the chinese government attaches great importance to the protection of intellectual property rights .
in the early days of reform and opening up , china began to establish an ipr system . through more than 20 years of efforts , a relatively complete ipr legal system has been formed , an ipr protection system combining judicial and administrative law enforcement has been established , and a great deal of work has been done in ipr protection , thus making an important contribution to promoting scientific and technological progress and economic and social development .
mankind has entered the information society in the 21 st century , and the scientific and technological revolution will promote the development of social productive forces with an unprecedented tremendous motive force .
further improving china 's ipr system and strengthening international exchanges and cooperation in ipr protection work are the requirements for china to open wider to the outside world in the new century , as well as the requirements for building a socialist modern country and realizing the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation .
we are willing to work together with other countries in the world to establish a fair and reasonable intellectual property system that is conducive to promoting the development of science and technology and the economy of all countries , and to create a good environment for all mankind to respect knowledge , advocate science , and protect intellectual property rights .
speeding up the institutionalization of the SCO is the most important task facing the SCO at present .
thanks to the efforts of all parties concerned , great progress has been made in preparing for the establishment of the secretariat and the regional anti - terrorist organization .
we will continue to make efforts to ensure that the secretariat is officially activated within this year and that a regional anti - terrorist body is established at an early date .
in order to show the great importance it attaches to the SCO , the chinese government , as the host country of the SCO secretariat , has decided to provide the secretariat with office accommodation free of charge .
in the future , we will continue to provide strong support for the smooth work of the secretariat .
deepening and expanding security cooperation has always been the focus of the work of the SCO .
