economic cooperation is an important foundation and priority direction of the Shanghai Cooperation Organization .
education is the cornerstone of modern civilization .
to improve the quality of our people and enhance our overall national strength , we must vigorously develop education .
the impact of rural education is extensive and has a bearing on the overall situation of rural economic and social development .
since the beginning of reform and opening up , tremendous and profound changes have taken place in china 's urban and rural areas , which are inextricably linked to the development of education , especially rural education .
the implementation of the household contract responsibility system in rural areas has greatly liberated the productive forces .
one of the fundamental reasons why advanced and practical agricultural technology can be popularized on a large scale , why township and town enterprises have emerged suddenly , and why the surplus rural labor force can be transferred in large numbers to coastal areas and cities and towns is that there are hundreds of millions of rural labor force who have received compulsory education as the foundation and support , and the great achievements made in popularizing compulsory education in rural areas are undeniable .
at present , china 's agriculture and rural economy are at a crucial stage of development . the development of high - quality , high - efficiency , ecological , and safe agriculture , the expansion of industrialized agricultural operations , and the transfer of surplus rural labor force are all in urgent need of comprehensively improving the quality of rural labor force .
the rise of the new scientific and technological revolution in the world and the promotion of building a moderately prosperous society in an all - round way have set higher demands on the scientific and cultural quality and ideological and moral quality of the vast rural population .
without the all - round improvement of peasants ' quality in rural areas , it will be very difficult to achieve a well - off life in an all - round way .
we must fully understand the basic , leading and overall role of rural education in building a moderately prosperous society in an all @-@ round way .
