Shenzhen implements SARS health quarantine for incoming and outgoing drivers
Xinhua news agency , Shenzhen , january 8 ( li nanling , hongwen ) - in order to effectively prevent the spread of infectious atypical pneumonia through the Shenzhen port and protect people 's health , the Shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau recently issued a public announcement , deciding to comprehensively implement health and quarantine measures such as taking body temperature and filling out health and quarantine declaration cards for entry and exit drivers at Huanggang , wenjindu , and shatoujiao land ports from the 9th .
it has been learned that due to the relatively large number of entry and exit vehicles at the Shenzhen port , such as the average number of daily entry and exit vehicles at Huanggang port and the number of vehicles at wenjindu port , it is quite difficult not only to ensure the smooth operation of the port but also to carry out health quarantine on all drivers .
in order to do a good job in checking the body temperature of entry and exit drivers and collecting health and quarantine declaration cards , the Shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has overcome all kinds of difficulties . in addition to sending additional personnel to the front line of the port , the Shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has recently urgently recruited more than 250 people . after conducting intensive training , all of them have been sent to the front line of the port to ensure the safety and smoothness of the port . at the same time , the Shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has also purchased 60 portable infrared rapid thermometers to meet the needs of the work .
the Shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau drew the attention of all relevant units and entry - exit drivers to the fact that the " entry - exit health quarantine declaration card " can be obtained at work points where the inspection and quarantine departments at various ports renew the " inspection and quarantine supervision book for entry - exit vehicles and goods ( persons ) " or at work points where the body temperature is measured and the health quarantine declaration card is collected .
at the same time , the bureau appealed to relevant units and entry - exit drivers to work together to do a good job in this work , effectively prevent the spread of sars through the Shenzhen port , and protect people 's health .
( international ) US Dollar Falls Again
Xinhua news agency , new york , january 8 , under the influence of a speech by the president of the european central bank , the us dollar 's exchange rate fell back to a low on the 8 th after a short - lived recovery on the 7 th .
Jean - Claude Trichet , governor of the european central bank , commented on the same day that the high euro exchange rate has had a negative impact on european enterprises ' exports , but he believes that the impact of the euro 's appreciation has been partly offset by the gradual recovery of the world economy and the turn of consumer demand .
he also pointed out that the strong euro also played a positive role in price stability in the euro zone to a certain extent , so the european central bank decided to maintain the original interest rate level .
investors saw the comments as a sign that euro zone officials were not worried about the appreciation of the euro , so they sold off the us dollar one after another , causing the us dollar to fall against other major western currencies across the board and the pound once rose to an 11 - year high against the us dollar .
the euro rose from 1.2640 to 1.2761 , the pound rose from 1.8180 to 1.8320 , reaching 1.8354 , the yen fell from 106.27 to 106.17 , and the dollar fell from 1.2398 to 1.2267 .
