according to huangshan city police , there are seven backbone members of Zhang Haiyang and other criminal gangs , two of whom are mistresses of Zhang Haiyang and all of whom are Jiangxi nationals .
since 1993 , the gang has been on the run in more than 10 prefectures and cities in Anhui 's huangshan , anqing , Jiangxi 's Fuzhou , jingdezhen , Zhejiang , and other provinces . in the past 10 years , there have been seven murders in robbery alone , six innocent people have been killed , and two of them have been mutilated by Zhang seawater mistresses .
