the two murders aroused the attention of the public security organs of huangshan city , and the ministry of public security listed the gang as supervising the handling of the cases .
on 18 january 2003 , huangshan city police arrested Zhang seawater , the main criminal suspect , and yu , his lover 's wife , in jingdezhen . subsequently , cao runxiang , Zhang guoxin , Chen wenwen , wu changlan , and other criminal suspects were also brought to justice one after another .
Zhang had been in prison for 23 years , and other criminal members were his relatives , fellow inmates , and lovers .
( international ) two black boxes of red sea crashed passenger plane found
Xinhua news agency , Cairo , january 17 , a joint Egyptian-french maritime search and rescue team recovered the first black box of the crashed passenger plane in the red sea on the 16 th and found the second black box of the crashed passenger plane in the bottom of the sea on the 17 th .
Sami hamdi , head of the Egyptian search and rescue team , said that the second black box recording the sound of the plane 's cockpit was being salvaged by the french diving robot Scorpio and was expected to be salvaged early on the 18th local time .
the two black boxes were found more than 1,000 meters underwater , about 30 meters apart .
the first black box , which will be decrypted and analyzed by a laboratory of egypt 's ministry of civil aviation , records all kinds of technical data prior to the plane crash , said Shakhr Zinjarada , head of egypt 's accident investigation committee .
although the black box looked badly damaged , Gilarda said it was in good condition .
the two so - called black boxes on the plane were actually light yellow in appearance .
according to the design , they can continuously send signals for 30 days after falling 6,000 meters to enable rescuers to determine their position and carry out salvage operations .
the plane that crashed in Red Sea waters belonged to Egypt &apos;s private Frash Airlines .
the Boeing 737 crashed into the red sea shortly after taking off from the Egyptian tourist resort of Sharm el - Sheikh on the 3 rd of this month , killing 148 people , including 134 french , one Moroccan and 13 Egyptian crew members .
Egyptian and french experts believe that the plane crash was caused by a technical malfunction rather than a terrorist attack or explosion , and finding the two black boxes on board will help solve the mystery .
breakthrough in ultra-low temperature finger preservation and replantation technology in China
Xinhua news agency , Jinan , january 18 ( reporter su Wanming ) - the severed finger successfully preserved in liquid nitrogen at -196 degrees celsius was replanted alive after surgery .
Chinese scholars have announced a major breakthrough in ultra-low temperature preservation and replantation of severed fingers .
a few days ago , the department of hand and foot surgery of Shandong provincial hospital successfully reimplanted a severed finger ( which has been preserved for five days in ultra - low temperature liquid nitrogen at -196 degrees celsius ) . this is the second case since the hospital successfully reimplanted the severed finger ( which was preserved for 81 days in liquid nitrogen at -196 degrees celsius ) last year .
the consultation report of the medical and health science and technology project of the ministry of health confirmed that the replantation of severed fingers after ultra - low temperature preservation has so far succeeded in only two cases in the world .
Wang zengtao , director of the hand and foot surgery department of Shandong provincial hospital , announced : after a lot of animal experimental research and the clinical application of two cases , we have preliminarily mastered the technique of ultra - low temperature preservation of severed fingers .
Wang zengtao said : compared with the heart , kidneys , and other organs , the composition and structure of fingers are more complicated . they contain blood vessels , nerves , tendons , skin , bones , joints , ligaments , and other tissues and are a kind of composite tissue .
the technique of ultra-low temperature preservation and application of severed finger involves a series of complicated links , such as preparation of refrigeration solution , organ freezing procedure , rewarming , replantation and prevention and treatment of reperfusion injury .
the mastery of this technique provides an important reference for the long-term preservation and successful resurrection of other human organs .
( international ) Greek foreign minister urges Greece , turkey to reduce military spending simultaneously
Xinhua news agency , Athens , january 17 ( reporter Wen xinnian ) - Greek foreign minister and president of the ruling panhellenic socialist movement Papandreou called on Greece and turkey on the 17th to gradually reduce their military spending in proportion .
he said that if the pan - Greek social movement wins the Greek general election on march 7 , he will make this policy an important foreign policy objective of the government .
speaking at a mass rally ahead of his campaign in northeastern Greece , Papandreou said that relations between Greece and turkey have improved markedly in recent years and have entered an all - new historical period .
he said : although not all issues have been resolved , new conditions have been created and the path of negotiations has been established .
he believes that 2004 will be a decisive year for formulating peace and security policies in the region .
Greece and turkey are both NATO members . however , there are conflicts of interest and contradictions between the two sides on issues such as the delimitation of the Aegean sea territorial waters , airspace , island continental shelf , and Cyprus , and this has also affected the normalization of relations between the two countries .
in recent years , Greece has pursued a policy of improving relations with turkey and no longer obstructed turkey 's accession to the european union , thus greatly improving bilateral relations .
( international ) china , argentina sign economic and technological cooperation agreement
Xinhua news agency , Tirana , january 19 ( reporter wang hongqi and Chen feng ) - the agreement on economic and technological cooperation between the chinese government and the Albanian government was signed in Tirana on the 19th . Chinese ambassador to Albania tian Changchun and Albanian vice foreign minister haidaga signed the agreement on behalf of the two governments respectively .
according to the agreement , china will provide Albania with free assistance worth 15 million yuan for economic and technological cooperation projects agreed upon by the two governments or for the provision of general materials by the chinese side to Albania .
after the signing ceremony , Khaidaraga thanked the chinese government for providing free assistance and congratulated the chinese people on the spring festival .
he said : the signing of this agreement shows the friendship and close cooperation between argentina and china in various fields .
in the future , the friendly and cooperative relations established between the two countries on the basis of mutual trust will be further strengthened .
Tian Changchun said : China has provided free assistance to Albania to express the friendly feelings of the chinese government and people toward the Albanian government and people , and at the same time to embody the traditional friendship and cooperation between china and Albania .
( international ) us troops in iraq kill 3 non-Iraqi Arabs
Xinhua news agency report of january 19th from Baghdad ( by staff reporter li jizhi and nie xiaoyang ) - Iraqi police disclosed on the 19th that two Yemenis and a Syrian were killed in a weapons search operation conducted by us troops stationed in iraq in the southern suburbs of Baghdad on the same day .
police said the three men were found in a search for a terrorist stronghold , and when the other side refused to surrender , the us military opened fire and killed them .
the US military then searched the house and seized a number of rifles , grenades and explosives .
the us military also arrested a Yemeni woman at the scene .
US and Iraqi officials believe that some foreign religious extremists are crossing the porous border into iraq and collaborating with anti - us forces in iraq to launch terrorist attacks against coalition occupation authorities and pro - us Iraqis .
on the 18th , a suicide bomber detonated a powerful car bomb in front of the coalition headquarters in central Baghdad , killing 24 people and injuring more than 100 others . the majority of the victims were Iraqis .
( international ) Silicon Valley Unemployment Decline heralds Recovery of US High @-@ tech Industries
Xinhua news agency , los Angeles , january 19 ( reporter Yan Liang ) - an influential economic development research institute in the silicon valley region of the united states recently issued a report saying that the unemployment rate in silicon valley is falling rapidly .
this is a clear signal that high - tech industries in the region are beginning to recover .
in its annual report " silicon valley 2004 economic index , " the nonprofit silicon valley joint venture said that the unemployment rate in the silicon valley region dropped from 10% in the previous year to 5% in the second quarter of 2003 .
according to the report , the unemployment rate will continue to decline as high - tech industries gradually recover .
the current challenge for Silicon Valley &apos;s economic development is the need for a large number of highly trained and highly skilled workers to fill new jobs in the future .
the report said that among the various high - tech industries in silicon valley , the unemployment rate in the biotechnology industry is the lowest and the recovery momentum is most evident . in 2003 , the silicon valley biotechnology industry attracted the same amount of venture investment as the computer software industry for the first time .
the report believes that the biotechnology industry will play an increasingly important role in the economic development of the silicon valley region .
the report also showed that between the second quarter of 2002 and the second quarter of 2003 , the average salary of employees in the silicon valley region declined for the third consecutive year , but the decline rate dropped to 1.5% from 6% in the previous year .
Silicon valley is still a wealthy region in the united states . the average annual salary of the labor force in the region is $ 62,400 , 60% higher than the average in the united states as a whole .
however , the consumption level of this region is 47% higher than that of the whole country .
