not long ago , Taiwan president Chen shui - Bian [ Chen Shuibian ] went to a rally somewhere in the north to shout " frozen garlic " and when he was elected , half of the people in Taiwan actually refused to give face to him and shouted " the local people have many relatives and friends who have invested in the mainland . the delay of the three direct links and the lack of achievements in financial and economic policies have all made many people feel uneasy .
if there are no surprises , when Taiwan 's presidential election enters the countdown time , judging from the public opinion poll to the underground intersection , it should be assumed that Chen shui - Bian and lu will be defeated .
